<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.4">
<l>kaṭalu malaiyum vicumpun tuḻāyempōl</l>
<l>cuṭarkko ḷirāppakaṟ ṟuñcāyā ṟaṇvāṭā</l>
<l>yaṭalkoḷ paṭaiyāḻi yammāṉaik kāṇpāṉī</l>
<l>yuṭalanō yuṟṟāyō vūḻitō ṟūḻiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Stirring sea and mountain and sky, like us,</l>
<l>seized by heat you don’t sleep day [or] night, cool north wind.</l>
<l>[longing] to see the lord with the discus as deathly seizing weapon,</l>
<l>do you have bodily pain aeon after aeon?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
